data.title: Blue Veins Organization
data.text:
Blue Veins is working in Pakistan since 1999 and has over one decade of experience in project implementation, management, lobbying, awareness campaign, community outreach and has implemented over 250 projects funded by international and national funding agencies. Blue Veins is an award-winning organization based in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa (KP) province of Pakistan committed to build, strengthen and galvanize women & transgender person's collective power for a just and sustainable world â€“ for all.

Blue Veins envisions a world free from violence and discrimination and where every individual lives with dignity and is equally empowered to reach their fullest potential.

Our mission is to work together in harmony with a higher spirit to improve the quality of life of women, children, and transgender to establish a people-centered framework for empowerment, sustainable health, and a social development to guide and build up a culture of cooperation and partnership and to respond to the immediate needs of those who are vulnerable.
